[node name="Level3" type="Node3D"]
editor_description = "Room 03 — Full Circuit. Ball enters front-left; a bank bumper forces an angled first kick around it. A short domino run threads past the bumper toward the gear, which hands off to a wire node, which detonates a vial tucked in a back-right nook. Real level design (asymmetric room, off-axis objects, one aim decision) — not a straight-line placeholder."

